{"tid":1779125,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC: WTO上訴機構正式停擺，美國可放開手腳打貿易戰","createTime":"2019-12-11T12:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T13:15:15.000Z","uid":279401,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24e711f8f96dd6015e71a1b1676b8b6174d03424","tid":1779125,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"解決國家間的貿易爭端是世界貿易組織（WTO）最重要的功能之一。從星期三（12月11日）起，這項功能正式停擺。<br />\n<br />\n為了解決成員國的經濟糾紛，WTO設置了爭端解決機構（DSB），成員國申訴後，派出爭端處理小組，調查後給出裁定。<br />\n<br />\n對裁定不滿的成員國可以向上訴機構提出上訴，上訴機構有七名常設法官，法官們作出的裁決相當於WTO的「終審判決」，因此該機構也被看作WTO的「最高法院」。<br />\n<br />\n而上訴機構僅剩三名成員在任，其中兩名即美國籍法官托馬斯&middot;格雷厄姆、印度籍法官巴提亞，將於11日屆滿卸任，只剩下一名中國籍法官趙宏，已無法達到最低三人的議事和審查人數。因此停擺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/business-50741543?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fbusiness-50741543%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAKkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=ef35c1a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fbusiness-50741543%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&h=1ae51349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/business-50741543?__twitter_impression=true</a>"},{"pid":"8d4e3e678c218ec48abf61b94acc541dbe928e73","tid":1779125,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"【Twitter要人!!】美加議員人權日tweet集合list!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1779138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1779138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要人入去推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]